Paper: hep-th/9803181

Date: 1998-03-23

Title: Generalized BFT Formalism of Electroweak Theory in the Unitary Gauge

Authors: Yong-Wan Kim, Young-Jai Park and Sean J. Yoon

Comments: 14 pages, Latex, no figures

Journal-ref: J.Phys. G25 (1999) 1783-1791

We systematically embed the SU(2)$\times$U(1) Higgs model in the unitarygauge into a fully gauge-invariant theory by following the generalized BFTformalism. We also suggest a novel path to get a first-class Lagrangiandirectly from the original second-class one using the BFT fields.